HEADWORD: Nudum pactum
<hw>Nu"dum pac"tum</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[L., a nude pact.]</ety>
<fld>(Law)</fld> <def>A bare, naked contract, without any consideration
and therefore unenforceable in a court of law.</def>
<rj><au>Tomlins.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

